            },
            "text": "„Ç™„Éó„Ç∑„Éß„É≥ 1"
          },
          {
            "tag": "div",
            "attributes": {
              "class": "dropdown-item",
              "data-dropdown-item": "true",
              "data-value": "option2",
              "style": "padding: 8px 16px; cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;"
            },
            "text": "„Ç™„Éó„Ç∑„Éß„É≥ 2"
